DOWNLOAD AND INSTALLATION
-------------------------

## Download repository
svn checkout http://bioinformatics-misc.googlecode.com/svn/branches/genomeGraphs genomeGraphs
cd genomeGraphs

## Optional: delete previous installation build
python setup.py clean --all

## User specific installation. No needs to admin rights:
python setup.py install --user --install-scripts $HOME/bin/

## Install for entire system
python setup.py install

TEST AND EXAMPLES
-----------------

## Some examples
genomeGraphsDemo.py tmp/

